text: Anthony Taylor (17 June 1882 - 16 November 1932) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 3 metre springboard event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:1932 deaths Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
